name: Axure RP Widget Library File
summary: Learn about .RPLIB files and view a list of programs that open them.

content: Axure RP widget libraries can be used for emulating the look and feel of different platforms. For example, custom widget libraries may contain icons or buttons that look like Android or iPhone user interfaces.
You can double-click an RPLIB file to install the new visual elements. Note that widgets from earlier versions of the software may not be compatible with later versions.
